CBRE are pleased to present 1214 & 1222 Rockingham Road, Naval Base, a secure long term investment on two titles in a core industrial locality.

The properties are leased to Integrated Container Logistics for a term expiring 22nd November 2023 at a commencement rent of $625,000pa net.

The property is situated 34km* south of the Perth CBD via Russell Road, 5.5km* by road to the Australian Marine Complex and 23km* south of Rous Head via Leach Highway.

Naval Base is strategically located nearby the established markets of Henderson to the west and Kwinana/Rockingham to the south. It is also located adjacent to Latitude 32, a master planned industrial estate that over time is expected to be one of Perthâ€™s largest and most strategic estates.

This property represents an extremely long term strategic investment in an area which is set to have future growth prospects.

We recommend you give this offering due consideration.

CBRE have the pleasure in offering for sale this opportunity to purchase a 'half acre'* of land with improvements located in the growing southern corridor.

Improvements include a house converted into offices plus a usable work shed of 300sqm* (STCA).

The yard is sealed bitumen and the property is securely fenced.

Please call the selling agent to discuss in more detail and arrange an inspection.
